edu.uidaho.junicon.interpreter.interpreter

Class PropertiesExtender

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uidaho.junicon.interpreter.interpreter.PropertiesExtender
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPropertiesExtender
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Environment

    public class PropertiesExtender
extends Object
implements IPropertiesExtender
    PropertiesExtender extends Properties with setters for changeagble delegation of defaultProperties, as well as load() and store() methods that operate on strings. Like Properties, the constructor allows a default Properties to be specified.
